<br>
By the time you're done killing the other 3 off, the druid won't understand why you're scolding him.  It's like training an animal.  If the dog does something wrong and you yell at him 5 minutes later, he won't know what the hell you're talking about.  There's a reason druids were given wolf form. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uclaudshadowflare.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ClaudShadowflare</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/20/02 11:57:12 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1218.topic&index=38>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: DAMN FUCKING DR00D</span><hr size=1> Toxx-<br>
<br>
1) A lot of us prefer to be left alone while quadding.  If I die, I prefer to have all of the responsibility rest on my shoulders rather than some druid who tried to &quot;help&quot;.  I don't mind at all if people ask if they can help; I'll tell them no and move along with my quad.<br>
<br>
2) Ensnare is about ~5% slower than Atol's.  Look it up in spell.dat.<br>
<br>
3) I run out of range to snare mobs that snare missed/resisted on, and it's a very common if not the most oft used tactic for dealing with snare resists.  Wyverns only warp back if they are below 10% health, running, and you are out of range.  Otherwise, they walk back to their spawn points.  Doing this is not an open invitation for &quot;help&quot;.<br>
<br>
4) Hotkeys that are announced every 15 minutes about how you shouldn't help someone piss people off because they grow annoying.  You have to use them every 15 minutes at least or people who are new to the zone remain uneducated.<br>
<br>
If you want help when you can't handle a quad, fine.  I don't, and I don't think it means that I shouldn't be playing this game because I don't like other people coming in and breaking up my quads because they want to be helpful.  Often, helpful people are fucking idiots.  Let the responsibility for my mistakes rest on my shoulders so I don't have to glare at you (or cuss you out as case may call for).<br>
<br>
Now, just to draw up a point-  You're KoS to a set of guards, but your race is normally accepted by them.  A monk sees you in trouble, so they train the guards over to you to help, getting you killed in the process.  Are they being helpful?<br>
<br>
It's always nice to ask before doing. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=1218.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=1218.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=1218.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=1218.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=1218.topic&start=101&stop=114>6</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showPrevMessage?topicID=1218.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showNextMessage?topicID=1218.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1218.topic&index=38><img src=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.emailToFriend?topicID=1218.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.threadControl?topicID=1218.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1218.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a hre